io.fluo.mapreduce

Class FluoMutationGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.fluo.mapreduce.FluoMutationGenerator

  • public class FluoMutationGenerator
extends Object
    This class generates Accumulo mutations that are in the Fluo data format. This class is intended to be used with AccumuloOutputFormat or BatchWriter inorder to seed an initialized Fluo table on which no transactions have executed.
